-- UniCredit Chief Profumo Says the Bank `Has No Problem' With Stress Tests
-- Flavia Rotondi
-- 2010-07-08T10:08:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/unicredit-chief-profumo-says-the-bank-has-no-problem-with-stress-tests.html

          
          
             UniCredit SpA Chief Executive Officer
Alessandro Profumo said Italy’s biggest bank “has no problem”
with stress tests, speaking to reporters in Rome today.  
 UniCredit expects to pass the stress tests, he said. Italy
is in better shape than other countries, he added.  
